thursday at a mortuary near princess grace hospital 
on friday a palace spokesman said the coffin was closed and 
taken to the palace for a private family mass 
the funeral service is scheduled for late saturday morning at a 
115yearold cathedral situated just below the palace it can 
accommodate more than 2000 people 
