casiraghis and the royal family were at odds about whether the 
funeral and burial should be in monaco or italy 
the speedboat championships in which casiraghi was seeking to 
defend his world title were canceled after crews from the other 41 
boats withdrew 
casiraghi had been racing at worldclass level since 1984 he 
had told friends he planned to quit after this season 
casiraghis death came eight years after carolines mother 
princess grace was killed in a car accident 
he and caroline were married on dec 29 1983 in a civil 
ceremony they had three children 
