journey if one of the satellites upperstage engines fails for 
instance the spacecraft and its plutonium generator could come 
crashing through the atmosphere 
the emergency team is prepared to rush anywhere in the world 
that the generator might fall jackson said 
officials of the national aeronautics and space administration 
