the first us edition published under the title guinness book 
of world records appeared in 1956 french and german language 
versions quickly followed 
the book has been translated into japanese spanish danish 
norwegian dutch portuguese czech hebrew serbocroatian 
icelandic slovenian greek indonesian chinese turkish hindi 
malay arabic thai tamil telugu malayalam kannada and 
