encephalitis is an inflammation of the brain that causes fever 
sore throat headaches confusion and muscular weakness in severe 
cases of this incurable disease it causes convulsions coma and 
death the st louis strain of the disease is named for the city 
where it was discovered in 1933 
many people who get infected may not have a disease they can 
