4yearold government on thursday noble organized a private army 
after taking part in a failed coup in december 
he surrendered early saturday after trying to sneak out of the 
military garrison he captured two days earlier 
government must now take the strongest possible measures to 
ensure that this become the last challenge that military rebels 
