new heart but that the lgionnaires infection was compromising his 
respiratory system 
legionnaires disease got its name from a 1976 outbreak at an 
american legion convention in philadelphia 
the sometimesfatal disease is caused by a common bacteria that 
grows in water including that in airconditioning ducts 
