cleanup at hazardous waste sites will cease 
social security offices will accept no new applications 
border inspections will be delayed 
in one agency after another thousands of federal employees 
would no longer be able to serve public tasks necessary for the 
public good 
the people of america did not send their representatives to 
washington to produce these consequences 
