activists who wanted to prevent nasa from launching the 
nuclearpowered ulysses the action in a washington federal court 
cleared the way for launch preparations to continue 
two demonstrators opposed to the radioactive cargo on discovery 
were arrested friday morning at the kennedy space center 
six hours after launch discoverys fiveman crew was scheduled 
