designed to rocket itself out of earth orbit for a roundabout 
voyage that eventually will enable it to study the unexplored polar 
regions of the sun 
young said discoverys mission would be unaffected by any 
government shutdown resulting from the federal budget dispute he 
said funds for the mission had already been set aside and notices 
had gone out that all employees were to report to work 
the mood of the team is confident and thats despite 
distractions and disappointments recently said launch director 
