engine compartment of the shuttle atlantis 
when the craft was hoisted from a horizontal to a vertical 
position the beam clanked around inside the compartment causing 
up to 25 dents and dings none of the damage was believed serious 
sieck said and atlantis is still scheduled for a mission in 
november 
the beam is normally used to support a work platform used when 
the shuttle is being processed on the ground 
