measures price movements on all outstanding treasury issues with 
maturities of a year or longer rose 068 to 115531 
yields on threemonth treasury bills fell to 725 percent as the 
discount tumbled 9 basis points to 703 percent yields on 
sixmonth bills fell to 742 percent as the discount dropped was 
down 6 basis points to 707 percent yields on oneyear bills fell 
to 749 percent as the discount dropped 3 basis points to 701 
percent 
a basis point is onehundredth of a percentage point the yield 
is the annualized return on an investment in a treasury bill the 
discount is the percentage that bills are selling below the face 
value which is paid at maturity 
the federal funds rate the interest rate banks charge each 
other on overnight loans was quoted at 7 1516 percent down from 
8 316 percent late thursday 
